  "texts": [
    "First, the LLM must faithfully follow instructions, which proves difficult since modern LLMs like ChatGPT are aligned with human values.",
    "This alignment acts as a safeguard, preventing the execution of harmful or ill-intended instructions.",
    "Prior research [31] illustrates that specific prompt patterns can successfully persuade LLMs to carry out instructions, sidestepping direct malicious requests.",
    "Second, bypassing the moderation component is critical.",
    "Such component functions as protective barriers against malicious intentions."
  ]
}